\f0\fs24 \cf0 # App Store Screenshots \'97 Guide\
\
## Required Sizes\
\
| Device | Resolution | Required? |\
|--------|------------|-----------|\
| iPhone 6.7" (15 Pro Max) | 1290 x 2796 | Yes |\
| iPhone 6.5" (11 Pro Max) | 1242 x 2688 | Yes |\
| iPhone 5.5" (8 Plus) | 1242 x 2208 | Optional (recommended) |\
| iPad 13" (Pro) | 2048 x 2732 | If iPad support |\
\
> Tip: You only need to create the 6.7" screenshots. Apple now allows using the same images for 6.5" (they will be scaled).\
\
## The 6 Screenshots (Order = Priority)\
\
### Screenshot 1: Map with Service Providers  \
What to show: MapScreen with pins on the map, one provider sheet open at the bottom  \
Overlay Text EN: "Find service partners near you"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Open app \uc0\u8594  Tab "Map"  \
2. Navigate to a region with many providers (e.g., Baltic Sea/North Sea)  \
3. Tap a provider pin (sheet opens)  \
4. Take screenshot (Side button + Volume up)  \
\
### Screenshot 2: Boat Management  \
What to show: BoatDataScreen with one boat + photo  \
Overlay Text EN: "Your boat \'97 all data in one place"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Tab "Boat" \uc0\u8594  Select a boat with photo and filled-in data  \
2. Scroll so name, photo, type, and some details are visible  \
3. Take screenshot  \
\
### Screenshot 3: Equipment & Maintenance  \
What to show: Maintenance screen with equipment items (due + upcoming)  \
Overlay Text EN: "Stay on top of maintenance"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Tab "Maintenance"  \
2. Show the list with color-coded items (red = overdue, orange = upcoming, green = ok)  \
3. Expand one item so buttons "Service" + "Spare Parts" are visible  \
4. Take screenshot  \
\
### Screenshot 4: AI Assistant  \
What to show: ChatScreen with a question + answer  \
Overlay Text EN: "Ask the AI assistant \'97 it knows your boat"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Tab "Assistant" (or AI button)  \
2. Ask a question like "Which oil does a Volvo Penta D2-40 need?"  \
3. Wait for the answer  \
4. Take screenshot (showing question + answer)  \
\
### Screenshot 5: Service Provider Search  \
What to show: ServiceSearchFromMaintenance with filter chips and results list  \
Overlay Text EN: "Search by category and brand"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Maintenance screen \uc0\u8594  Expand an equipment item \u8594  "Service"  \
2. The search shows filter chips (category + brand) and the provider list  \
3. Take screenshot  \
\
### Screenshot 6: Shop / Spare Parts  \
What to show: ProviderShopSearchView or ShopView with products  \
Overlay Text EN: "Order spare parts from your equipment list"  \
How to capture:  \
1. Maintenance screen \uc0\u8594  Expand equipment \u8594  "Spare Parts"  \
2. Show search results with product tiles  \
3. Take screenshot  \
\
