## Checklist Before Upload\
\
- [ ] 6 screenshots per device size  \
- [ ] EN variants (or only one language if using a single store)  \
- [ ] No alpha transparency (PNG, no alpha channel)  \
- [ ] No iPhone status bar artifacts (or intentionally cropped)  \
- [ ] Text is readable even in thumbnail view  \
- [ ] First screenshot = strongest feature (map/service search)}